item.title: Workshop 5: Vue.js Cont.
item.description: It is advised to have general knowledge of how Vue.js + Vuex works before proceeding. Open a clean directory and clone the working repository (if not already done): git clone https://github.com/Pwntus/mic-workshops.git Next, navigate to mic-workshops/workshops/05 and run npm i: cd mic-workshops/workshops/05 && npm i Wait for it to complete before continuing.
